column1: On Transition ('TXNS') table, initial state is shown in the leftmost column, following state is shown in other columns.
E.g. given initial state 0000 (none out, none on), 1000 (one out, none on) followed it 424,217 times in the input (games from 2000 through 2013)
Total shows how many times the first state occurred, so we can learn that 1000 occurred 424217/634825 or ~ 67% of the time, given initial state 0000.
